a.) The start will be by asking if he is an existing customer or a new user.

    i.) If it is a new customer, we will add customer of which we will store 
        Customer Name,Create a Customer account Number,Customer Deposits.
        The Customers will be added dynamically using the List and each element in the list would contain 
        his details which were mentioned above.

   ii.) If it is a existing customer we will be availing him to get the following facilities. 

b.) The existing Customer will be asked whether he want to do any transaction or will just check the account details.

c.) To access the Account details we will be using his account number.

d.) For Money Withdrawl we will be using a class which will update the money in the account after each transaction.

e.) Giving Account Statement after every withdrawl or deposit.

